column2: Sporadic showers- light wind- 50 F- water dark.
A lot of rain and snow melt--water is high.
A lot of rain this week--water is high. It's sunny today.
Not much rain- pretty hot outside.
Lake turning over. Very hot and no rain for a long time.
Lake has turned a lot of rain.  Lake is very green with lots of weed.  Humid weather.
sunny sunny sunny sunny sunny sunny
